original: Österberg, Johan Albert Fredrik, försäljningschef, Hyltebruk, f. 25/9/94 i Sthlm av J. Alfr. Ö. o. Anna Frank. G. 18 m. Titti Wahlberg, d. 46. Barn: Maud f. 19, g. m. avd:chef Sven Hill, Sthlm, Karin 25. — Stud. v. Krafftska sk. i Sthlm. Aff :res. spec. t. Engl. fr. 24. Korresp. h. A-B Axel Chris-tiernssons papp :avd. i Sthlm 11-24, försiäljn :chef v. Hyltebruk fr. 24. Ordf. i Hylteibr. tenniskl, Hall. idr:förb. tennissekt. Hobby: Tennis. Sv. Ten-nisförb. ftjm. Hall, idr:förb. ftjM, Hyltebr. tenniskl. guldplak.
translated: Österberg, Johan Albert Fredrik, sales manager, Hyltebruk, b. 25/9/94 in Stockholm to J. Alfr. Ö. and Anna Frank. Married 18 years with Titti Wahlberg, d. 46. Children: Maud b. 19, married to department manager Sven Hill, Stockholm, Karin 25. Studied at Krafftska school in Stockholm. Worked as a specialty representative for England from 1924. Corresponded with A-B Axel Christiernssons paper department in Stockholm from 1911-1924, became sales manager in Hyltebruk from 1924. Chairman of Hyltebruk tennis club, Halland sports association tennis sector. Hobby: tennis. Member of the Swedish Tennis Association, Halland Sports Association, Hyltebruk tennis club. Has been awarded a gold plaque.
